## Additional Rules (qa-specific)

11. **Clean working tree required.** If dirty, AskUserQuestion to offer commit/stash/abort before proceeding.
12. **One commit per fix.** Never bundle multiple fixes.
13. **Only modify tests when generating regression tests in Phase 8e.5.** Never modify CI config. Never modify existing tests — only create new test files.
14. **Revert on regression.** Fix makes things worse → `git revert HEAD` immediately.
15. **Self-regulate.** Follow WTF-likelihood heuristic. When in doubt, stop and ask.
